  "title": "Junior Conveyancing Lawyer | PQE | Degree | Telok Ayer | 5 Days | Up To $5.5K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title: Junior Conveyancing Lawyer</strong><br />Starting Salary: $5,500<br />Working Days: 5 days<br />Working Timing: 9:00 am to 6:00 pm<br />Working Location: Telok Ayer</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and review legal documents related to property transactions. These documents include sale and purchase agreements and loan agreements.</li><li>You will provide advice to clients on all aspects of buying or selling property. This includes legal issues, financial considerations, and contract matters.</li><li>Engage in negotiations with the other party’s lawyer for the Option to Purchase (OTP). Provide advice to clients on the conveyancing process and their rights and obligations.</li><li>Liaise with various parties involved in the transaction, including real estate agents, mortgage lenders, and other relevant stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree in Law </li><li>0 - 3 years of Post-Qualification Experience (PQE) in conveyancing or related<br />legal work.</li><li>Familiarity with property laws and conveyancing procedures.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
